                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230625-85-off490 t18230625-85-crimeloc493"></join>. The prisoner came in to buy eighteen yards of list; I went under the counter to get it, and during that time he drew this silk out of the window, through the rail; I missed it, went round the counter, and found it in his hand; he said he picked it off the ground to prevent its being damaged.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. The door shutting threw this silk off the rail, I picked it up, and put it on the rail again.</p>
               <p>
            
